sequenceDiagram
    participant K as Kline / Market Data
    participant F as FeaturePipeline
    participant W as Rolling Window
    participant T as TinyLLM Transformer
    participant S as SignalInterpreter
    participant R as Risk Layer

    K->>F: OHLCV, order book, news/event context
    F->>F: normalize + build 1024-d vector
    F->>W: append latest feature vector
    W->>W: keep last 16 steps
    W->>T: numeric sequence tensor
    T->>T: multi-head attention across time
    T->>S: signal embedding
    S->>R: direction, confidence, sizing hint
    R->>R: Kelly, drawdown, pretrade gates
    R-->>S: approved / rejected trade intent
